  "description": "Effort-focused S-curve arc. Begins in pure whisper \u2014 breathy, soft, intimate. Over 15 seconds the arc drives effort from pianissimo to fortissimo while synchrony builds. LFO1 slowly morphs the vowel from U (closed, whispered) to A (open, belted). The singer finds their voice.",
